#: ../../ref/states/startup.rst:8
msgid ""
"Sometimes it may be desired that the salt minion execute a state run when it"
" is started. This alleviates the need for the master to initiate a state run"
" on a new minion and can make provisioning much easier."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ref/states/startup.rst:12
msgid ""
"As of Salt 0.10.3 the minion config reads options that allow for states to "
"be executed at startup. The options are `startup_states`, `sls_list` and "
"`top_file`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ref/states/startup.rst:16
msgid ""
"The `startup_states` option can be passed one of a number of arguments to "
"define how to execute states. The available options are:"
msgstr ""

